        <mxCell id="s3-tasks" value="Tasks:&#10;- Implement AML compliance engine (risk scoring 0-100, Auditor review)&#10;- Build compliance audit dashboard with transaction flagging&#10;- Run Pylint, fix code quality issues, add inline comments&#10;- Deploy to Azure Container Apps via Terraform IaC&#10;- Write documentation and prepare final LMS submission" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#f57f17;fontSize=8;textAlign=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
